          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used for consultation and study and is a treatise on Hindu astronomy and mathematics and deals with the prediction and divination of events that affect the course of human life. A few astrological tables are drawn in the manuscript, some with numbers and letters and others left blank. Manuscript lacks an ending.</summary>
